Definition: pleasantness resulting from agreeable conditions
Example: a well trained staff saw to the agreeableness of our accommodations; he discovered the amenities of reading at an early age
Synonyms: adj, all, agreeable, disagreeableness, amenity, pleasantness, resulting, from, conditions, a, well, trained, staff, saw, to, the, of, our, accommodations, he, discovered, amenities, reading, at, an, early, age
Category: noun.attribute
